 the entire product lifecycle, working across development, business units, sales, marketing and sales enablement functions, including supporting the creation of any collateral that is needed for these activities. The position requires a strong presence at industry and partner events. Resposibilities Three or more years of architectural skills dealing with Cloud Native solutions that include Docker, Kubernetes, Multi-Cloud, Blockchain, IoT, Cognitive, Dev/Ops and Cloud Three or more years of migration strategies including host-based, hypervisor-based, storage-based, and re-implementation One or more years of experience with networking; for Cloud-Native; especially secure connectivity between on-premise and cloud One or more years of experience with Cloud Native High Availability approach; especially Multi-Zone Regions (MZR) Two or more years of experience with multi-cloud including AWS, Azure, and Google \u2013 experience with Azure and/or collaborating with Microsoft is strongly preferred Three or more years of experience building working relationships with decision-makers including portfolio managers, architects, and delivery teams Experience with commercial agreements and open source "
